{
  "name": "Miraggio - L1 & L2 Approval Webhook",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔐 Approval Webhook (L1 + L2)\n\n**One webhook handles all 4 cases:**\n- L1 + APPROVE → bill goes to PENDING_L2, L2 emailed\n- L1 + REJECT  → bill goes to REJECTED_L1, vendor notified\n- L2 + APPROVE → bill goes to PENDING_PAYMENT, finance gets bank details\n- L2 + REJECT  → bill goes to REJECTED_L2, vendor notified\n\n**Test URL (production):**\n`https://YOUR-N8N/webhook/approval?token=XYZ`\n\n**Before activating:**\n1. Replace `L2_APPROVER_EMAIL@miraggio.com` in 'Send L2 Email'\n2. Replace `FINANCE_TEAM_EMAIL@miraggio.com` in 'Notify Finance'\n3. Activate the workflow",
        "height": 380,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "9a880fd8-e46f-4491-8762-11852bbc9770",
      "name": "📋 SETUP",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
